OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late sunshine.
OL,7,FThen the rest of the night will be dry
OL,8,Fwith lengthy clear periods. A warm
OL,9,Fnight along the west coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FDry with plenty of sunshine.
OL,12,FBecoming very warm, locally hot.
OL,13,FCooler along the Caithness coast.
OL,14,FChance of a few showers in the west in
OL,15,Fthe late evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
